---

<main role="main">
  <picture  class="img-circle home-image">
   <source type="image/webp" srcset="/images/avatar-4-2022-400.webp">
   <source type="image/jpeg" srcset="/images/avatar-4-2022-400.jpg">
   <img src="/images/avatar-400.jpg" alt="Piet van Zoen">
  </picture>
  <h1 class="text-center">Hi, I&#39;m Piet.</h1>
  <p class="home-intro"><span>I build things for the web.<br>This is my website.</span></p>

  <div class="site-menu-home site-menu">
    <nav class="site-menu-list">
      <ol>
        {%- for item in site.menu -%}
        {%- if page.url != item.href -%}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ item.href }}">{{ item.name }}</a>
          </li>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </ol>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <p>Welcome! Hello! This is my little plot of the internet where I capture notes and thoughts on the things I&#8217;m interested in. (When ever I get around to writing anything.) This includes web development, all things command line, vim, cats, family, expat life, field recording, 3d printing, and general tinkering. </p>

  <p>Below are some of my favourite posts. Thanks for visiting. üôè</p>

  <ul>
    {%- for post in collections.featured -%}
    <li><a href="{{post.url}}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>

  <strong><a href="/notes">Browse all notes</a></strong>

</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <hr>
  {% include 'social-links.njk' %}
